column2: TINDAKMALAYSIA NETWORK SERVICES PLT (TINDAK MALAYSIA)

Election Commission of Malaysia (https://web.facebook.com/sprgovmy/videos/356852687479734/) (SPR), Tindak Malaysia (2024), Attorney General Chambers, Sinar Harian (https://www.google.com/url?q=https://www.sinarharian.com.my/article/678695/infografik/biodata-calon-prk-nenggiri&sa=D&source=editors&ust=1724041012022157&usg=AOvVaw0BymBp9FkGr6JX0bUlsuSW)

This is the non-gazetted official result from SPR. All police voters entitled to be early voters opted to be postal voters; hence, no early voting activity was required. Due to limitations of SPR Facebook live, full saluran result was not obtainable. Some of the Saluran level results for candidate votes and total valid votes were computed by Tindak Malaysia. TindakMalaysia Network Services PLT is not responsible for any errors or omissions arising from the original data or its derivatives
